(380, 'What is the Ministry of MSME\'s role?', 'The Ministry of MSME oversees the development and promotion of micro, small, and medium enterprises in India. It creates policies, implements schemes, and supports MSMEs through funding, training, and infrastructure assistance.', 'MSME / Udyam Registration', 'services-msme-udyam-registration', 1, '2026-01-21 10:43:28', '2026-01-21 10:43:28'),
(381, 'Can you explain what Udyog Aadhar is?', 'Udyog Aadhaar was a simplified registration process for MSMEs that has now been replaced by Udyam Registration. It allowed businesses to self-declare and register online for government benefits.', 'MSME / Udyam Registration', 'services-msme-udyam-registration', 1, '2026-01-21 10:43:28', '2026-01-21 10:43:28'),
(382, 'Why is the term \'Micro\' used in the context of MSME?', 'The term \'Micro\' refers to the smallest category in MSMEs, typically defined by low investment and turnover thresholds. It helps the government provide targeted support to very small businesses.', 'MSME / Udyam Registration', 'services-msme-udyam-registration', 1, '2026-01-21 10:43:28', '2026-01-21 10:43:28'),
(383, 'How does the Ministry of Micro differ from the Ministry of MSME?', 'There is no separate Ministry of Micro. The Ministry of MSME handles all micro, small, and medium enterprises under one umbrella, including policies, classifications, and schemes for micro-level businesses.', 'MSME / Udyam Registration', 'services-msme-udyam-registration', 1, '2026-01-21 10:43:28', '2026-01-21 10:43:28'),
(384, 'I saw a mention of \'fees for Udyam registration file.\' Is there a cost involved?', 'No, Udyam Registration is completely free of cost. Businesses can register themselves on the official portal without any fees or intermediaries.', 'MSME / Udyam Registration', 'services-msme-udyam-registration', 1, '2026-01-21 10:43:28', '2026-01-21 10:43:28'),
(385, 'Are any documents needed for the self-declaration during Udyam Registration?', 'No documents are required to be uploaded during self-declaration. However, Aadhaar is mandatory, and information like PAN and GST details may be validated automatically.', 'MSME / Udyam Registration', 'services-msme-udyam-registration', 1, '2026-01-21 10:43:28', '2026-01-21 10:43:28'),
(386, 'What advantages does Udyog Aadhaar registration offer to MSMEs?', 'It offered benefits like access to subsidies, eligibility for government schemes, easier access to credit, and protection against delayed payments. These are now offered under the Udyam system.', 'MSME / Udyam Registration', 'services-msme-udyam-registration', 1, '2026-01-21 10:43:28', '2026-01-21 10:43:28'),
(387, 'I\'ve heard about \'MSME classification.\' How was it determined in the past?', 'Earlier, MSMEs were classified based on investment in plant and machinery. Now, both investment and annual turnover are considered for classification as Micro, Small, or Medium.', 'MSME / Udyam Registration', 'services-msme-udyam-registration', 1, '2026-01-21 10:43:28', '2026-01-21 10:43:28'),
(388, 'Why is the Aadhaar number important for MSME registration?', 'Aadhaar is required for identity verification of the business owner during Udyam Registration. It ensures authenticity and links the registration to the rightful promoter.', 'MSME / Udyam Registration', 'services-msme-udyam-registration', 1, '2026-01-21 10:43:28', '2026-01-21 10:43:28'),
(389, 'What is the importance of the \'Udyog Aadhaar number\'?', 'The Udyog Aadhaar number served as a unique identifier for MSMEs to avail benefits. Though now replaced by Udyam Registration Number, it was used to track eligibility for schemes and subsidies.', 'MSME / Udyam Registration', 'services-msme-udyam-registration', 1, '2026-01-21 10:43:28', '2026-01-21 10:43:28'),
(390, 'Could you provide more information about the \'MSME sector\' in India?', 'The MSME sector forms the backbone of India’s economy, contributing significantly to employment, exports, and GDP. It includes manufacturing and service enterprises with varying levels of investment and turnover.', 'MSME / Udyam Registration', 'services-msme-udyam-registration', 1, '2026-01-21 10:43:28', '2026-01-21 10:43:28'),
